Riksbank’s Nyberg Says Krona ‘Will Never Be Swiss Franc’

-- B y   J o h a n   C a r l s t r o m
-- 
2011-09-29T07:55:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/riksbank-s-nyberg-says-krona-will-never-be-swiss-franc-.html
Swedish central bank Deputy
Governor Lars Nyberg said the krona will never become a
substitute for the Swiss franc as a haven currency. He made the
comments to reporters in  Stockholm  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Johan Carlstrom in Stockholm at 
 jcarlstrom@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tasneem Brogger at 
 tbrogger@bloomberg.net  